{"tid":1010382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與伊斯蘭教領袖親擁 教宗籲各宗教共同反戰","createTime":"2019-02-06T03:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T07:38:18.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"001b214e047bdc7a9387d52425f7b1387cd24ada","tid":1010382,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T03:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190205/_2019020514453973731.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190205%2F_2019020514453973731.jpg&h=2bef2cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n教宗歷史性訪問阿拉伯半島，並與回教領袖親擁。AP<br />\n教宗方濟各到訪阿拉伯半島展開為期3日訪問行程，是首名到訪阿拉伯半島的教宗。其間更與伊斯蘭教領袖會面，出席一個跨宗教會議。在出席跨信仰會議前，方濟各先到謝赫扎耶德大清真寺，與伊斯蘭領袖會面30分鐘。梵蒂岡表示，方濟各與伊斯蘭領袖討論不同文化如何加強互動，以達致對話及平。<br />\n<br />\n方濟各在會議上向阿聯酋皇室成員、官員、伊瑪目、穆夫提等數百人發表重要演說。他表示，信仰尋求和平，他祈求和平可以在世界上得到體現。他又表示，宗教領袖有義務反對戰爭，致力實踐對話，並負起責任，反對任何對戰爭的授權，實踐人與人之間的友愛。他又特別提到，目前在也門、敘利亞、伊拉克及利比亞的衝突，促請各國領袖抵抗暴力的洪流，他在會議上與埃及回教遜尼派大伊瑪目塔伊布簽訂「人類友愛」聯合聲明。<br />\n<br />\n羅馬教廷阿拉伯及伊斯蘭研究中心的科蒂尼教授表示，榮休的教宗本篤16世曾引用14世紀拜占庭帝國的文獻，批評伊斯蘭教先知穆罕默德，令雙方關係惡劣，而方濟各喜愛與別人交流，作風與本篤16世截然不同，認為有助天主教和伊斯蘭教破冰。<br />\n<br />\n教宗周二將在當地主持大型彌撒，是阿拉伯半島內首場教宗彌撒，預計有13.5萬人出席。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/926920-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E8%88%87%E4%BC%8A%E6%96%AF%E8%98%AD%E6%95%99%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96%E8%A6%AA%E6%93%81+%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E7%B1%B2%E5%90%84%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E5%8F%8D%E6%88%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F926920-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%2598%25AD%25E6%2595%2599%25E9%25A0%2598%25E8%25A2%2596%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E6%2593%2581%2B%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%2590%2584%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2588%25B0&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=7da718b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F926920-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%2598%25AD%25E6%2595%2599%25E9%25A0%2598%25E8%25A2%2596%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E6%2593%2581%2B%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%2590%2584%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2588%25B0&h=5242a4b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/926920-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E8%88%87%E4%BC%8A%E6%96%AF%E8%98%AD%E6%95%99%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96%E8%A6%AA%E6%93%81+%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E7%B1%B2%E5%90%84%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E5%8F%8D%E6%88%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n點解要咁咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197c3a47b894d507590e7f0e6646c97b5bd4e683","tid":1010382,"uid":109780,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T05:10:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾教宗"},{"pid":"65042f07647978eaa26aa02b84a46f2f4498efda","tid":1010382,"uid":16493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:22:07.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de092f269a9ad7339d704ef56a2082cd955baefc","tid":1010382,"uid":49316,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"197c3a47b894d507590e7f0e6646c97b5bd4e683","tid":1010382,"uid":109780,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T05:10:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾教宗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:35:47.000Z","msg":"包庇搞細路神父<br />\n<br />\n支那建交唔理地下教會友<br />\n<br />\n再去回教地方做show<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137d2ecb352a703c80765f9a616c121aacfb1375","tid":1010382,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:38:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6fc23e5bd